#X text 266 25 feedback delay line capable of handling up to 5 seconds.
inputs are signal \, delay time (ms) \, and feedback amount (which
defaults to 0.5) -jason plumb;
#X obj 105 25 inlet;
#X obj 166 24 inlet;
#X text 28 8 audio;
#X text 90 9 delay(ms);
#X text 168 10 feedback;
#X obj 26 222 *~ 0.5;
#X text 270 110 Interesting Delay Line patch from Jason Plumb. I made
it a bit more efficient by removing unnecessary stuff such as number
boxes between connections and changed the output control to a multiplication.
Jason Plumb had originally used a division but multiplications are
always preferred in computer programming. -Jesus H.;
